data.description: Step into contemporary comfort with this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath gem, a 2019 build that feels brand new. Boasting over 2,000 sqft, it offers spacious living. The kitchen features granite countertops, stained cabinets, newer appliances and a large pantry with an open view to the living room. All bedrooms are tucked away on the upper level for added privacy. Indulge in the primary bathroom's separate tub and shower, while oversized secondary bedrooms share a full bath. With a charming brick front and a private backyard, this home provides a perfect blend of style and tranquility. Conveniently located near schools, shopping, and more – it's an ideal modern haven.
